What Is a Jew? captures the astonishing diversity of the subpopulation ass=
ociated with New York=E2=80=99s intellectual elite but=2C in reality=2C sp=
anning a vast spectrum of inclinations=2C interests=2C and legacies. (One=
 can grasp that staggering range in reading Alfred Kazin=E2=80=99s poignan=
t reflections on the loneliness of being in a culture but not of it (https=
://www.brainpickings.org/2016/07/05/alfred-kazin-walker-in-the-city-love/?=
mc_cid=3Df476b8e46c&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) =2C penned amid Brooklyn=E2=80=99s=
